      "prompt": "Compute the implied EV/EBITDA multiple for this deal:\n  Enterprise value: $1.2 billion\n  LTM EBITDA: $150 million\nState the multiple to one decimal place. In the SAME response, explicitly include the abbreviation EV/EBITDA somewhere in your text.",
